channel.title: Case 155: first click npc not working?!?!
channel.description: I have no clue why but my case 155 just randomly stopped working. Any of the npcs that u could click talk-to and it opened a shop wont work anymore. Any of the npcs that would have a dialogue with you will not work anymore. I am 100% sure its not the shops or now the dialogue that is the error because they both work with other things, its case 155. Please help me, i've asked many times on this help section and not one person has answered me yet. :(
